w the Popup templates, update to version 0.1.6, then click on Elements, then Blocks, then filter for \'Popups\'.</p>\n";}i:11;a:5:{s:2:"id";i:1672;s:5:"title";s:29:"5 New Elementor Template Kits";s:4:"date";s:18:"24th December 2018";s:10:"categories";s:11:"New Content";s:7:"content";s:119:"<p>We released 5 new Template Kits for Elementor today, it brings us to a total of 65 Template Kits for Elementor!</p>\n";}i:12;a:5:{s:2:"id";i:1600;s:5:"title";s:41:"New Feature: Envato Button for Elementor!";s:4:"date";s:18:"13th December 2018";s:10:"categories";s:12:"New Features";s:7:"content";s:229:"<p>If you\'re running version 0.1.4 of our plugin, when you\'re in the Elementor Builder, you\'ll see the Envato Button, it\'ll open a modal so you can easily import any of our templates directly into the page you\'re working on!</p>\n";}i:13;a:5:{s:2:"id";i:1233;s:5:"title";s:30:"10 New Elementor Template Kits";s:4:"date";s:18:"19th November 2018";s:10:"categories";s:11:"New Content";s:7:"content";s:120:"<p>We released 10 new Template Kits for Elementor today, it brings us to a total of 60 Template Kits for Elementor!</p>\n";}i:14;a:5:{s:2:"id";i:943;s:5:"title";s:29:"5 New Elementor Template Kits";s:4:"date";s:17:"24th October 2018";s:10:"categories";s:11:"New Content";s:7:"content";s:119:"<p>We released 5 new Template Kits for Elementor today, it brings us to a total of 50 Template Kits for Elementor!</p>\n";}}', 'no');
